&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Data Platform Support Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team, supporting and maintaining our &lt;strong&gt;Azure Data Platform&lt;/strong&gt; ecosystem. This role requires experience in &lt;strong&gt;Azure SQL, Azure Data Factory (ADF), and Synapse Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;, along with exposure to &lt;strong&gt;Snowflake&lt;/strong&gt;. You will work closely with data Architects, data engineers, and customer services team to ensure the reliability, performance, and security of our data platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle incident management, root cause analysis, and implement preventive measures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure adherence to &lt;strong&gt;Data Platform Support SLAs and KPIs&lt;/strong&gt;, proactively monitoring and responding to incidents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and maintain &lt;strong&gt;Azure SQL databases&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring optimal performance and availability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support for &lt;strong&gt;Azure Data Factory (ADF)&lt;/strong&gt; pipelines, troubleshooting failures and optimizing workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and troubleshoot &lt;strong&gt;Azure Synapse Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;, including serverless and dedicated SQL pools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support for &lt;strong&gt;Spark Notebooks in Synapse&lt;/strong&gt;, troubleshooting execution failures and optimizing Spark jobs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support for &lt;strong&gt;Apache Spark and Delta Lake&lt;/strong&gt;, troubleshooting issues and ensuring performance optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support &lt;strong&gt;Snowflake&lt;/strong&gt; workloads and assist in integrating it within our data ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and troubleshoot &lt;strong&gt;ETL/ELT processes&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring data integrity and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with data engineers to optimize database queries, stored procedures, and indexing strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage &lt;strong&gt;data security, access control, and compliance&lt;/strong&gt; within the Azure Data Platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automate routine support tasks using &lt;strong&gt;PowerShell, Python, or Terraform&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with DevOps teams for &lt;strong&gt;CI/CD pipeline management and infrastructure as code (IaC)&lt;/strong&gt; deployments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support data governance and metadata management using &lt;strong&gt;Azure Purview&lt;/strong&gt; or other data cataloguing tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow internal processes and security guidelines to maintain data platform integrity and compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills &amp;amp; Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5+ years&lt;/strong&gt; of experience in a &lt;strong&gt;data platform support&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;database administration&lt;/strong&gt; role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong hands-on experience with &lt;strong&gt;Azure SQL, Data Factory, and Synapse Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with &lt;strong&gt;Azure Data Lake, Delta Lake, and storage management in a cloud environment&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
